Melena
Blatchford Score
If no liver, heart disease + no anemia, no vital signs or syncope - then can go home

Ulcer with Vessel
IV PPI BID (not drip or PO) x 72 hrs

No FCC/FPP if hemodynamically stable, hold DOAC/Coumadin and wait to < 2.5 to correct
If unstable, or > 5U loss/given then given FPP/FCC

If good control after bleed restart DOAC next day.
If not good control < 7-5 days restart (do not let it cessation more than this time frame)
